node.text: October in New York. The BEST trip. From Kelly & Ryan, a holiday shoot day in Brooklyn (more soon) and celebrating our Pumpkin Smash candle. I feel so lucky to get to do these things and it’s really because of you all 🧡 SO FREAKING excited for the the coming months and year. So many new things to share!! Thank you for the outpour of support! I say this all the time, but you really feel like family. And while the candle might be sold out now, it’s back in November, just in time for the holidays 🦃
